Sentencas: Chromium deposition and poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) cathodes of solid oxide fuel cells are investigated.
Titulo: Chromium Deposition and Poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: BSCF cathode shows an excellent and stable performance in the absence of metallic interconnects.
Titulo: Chromium Deposition and Poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: However, in the presence of a chromia-forming metallic interconnect performance of the BSCF cathodes degrades quickly.
Titulo: Chromium Deposition and Poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Chromium deposition was observed on the BSCF cathode surface after 1200 min polarization at 900 and 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Chromium Deposition and Poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The Cr2O3/SrO and Cr2O3/BaCO3 oxide couple study indicates that SrCrO4, BaCrO4, and BaCr2O4 start to form at temperatures above 500 degrees C.
Titulo: Chromium Deposition and Poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that BSCF cathode is not chromium-tolerant despite its superior activity for the O-2 reduction reaction.
Titulo: Chromium Deposition and Poisoning at Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ Cathode of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
